{"tid":1783168,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗指長者退休無收入　統計上視為貧窮：部份未必有經濟需要","createTime":"2019-12-14T14:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T15:11:59.000Z","uid":267488,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"864948eba106ec0707c77bc924edf009999dd973","tid":1783168,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"政府昨公布最近貧窮數字，被界定為貧窮人口的市民共有140.6萬人創新高；比率為20.4%，僅次於2009的20.6%，代表每五名市民，就有一人處於貧窮線以下。有政策介入後，去年貧窮長者人數達36萬，較前年新增2萬名貧窮長者。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗今日（14日）出席公開活動後稱，貧窮人口數據只參考家庭收入，不計算資產等因素，而在退休後沒有經濟收入，在統計上會被納入貧窮人口，「部份長者未必有經濟需要，數字演繹上要小心。」<br />\n<br />\n張建宗:退休無貧窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d851b5e7afbbd5ce40e5d88c5791f60cc21b47","tid":1783168,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e70f3262d14043e587a85d1b6571b320f0bd575f","tid":1783168,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"0收入之下先叫窮咪得囉<br />\n全港冇窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af00a0d40e86449e973e2e9d5d25ac32d62f677","tid":1783168,"uid":189328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">貧窮人口數據只參考家庭收入，不計算資產等因素，而在退休後沒有經濟收入，在統計上會被納入貧窮人口</span><br />\n<br />\n咁講李嘉誠都係貧窮人口喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28baf915628f408dca1b79d5875bfe4a9e62d7f0","tid":1783168,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5af00a0d40e86449e973e2e9d5d25ac32d62f677","tid":1783168,"uid":189328,"like":1,"dislike"